Description: Ness Eli Diaper Tote Bag Product description The Eli bag from ness bags is an all around great diaper bag. It's not too big and it's not too small. It's just the right size. Whether you are out and about running some quick errands or going out for a day trip, this is a great bag with many convenient and versatile features. Like all ness bags, each designer diaper bag brings together the best in fashion and function. You'll appreciate how versatile this bag is with adjustable straps allowing you to carry it in three ways. You can have your arms free to take care of your little one or accomplish your desired tasks. The Eli bag has three exterior pockets and three interior pockets to help keep you and your baby gear organized while you are on the go. Not only is this a fashionable and functional diaper bag, it is a product with a unique story from a very special company. Ness bags are named after the Hebrew word for miracle. And, each bag design is named for a special baby and its journey to survive birth, or an organization devoted to helping newborns and families in their struggle. The Eli bag is named after a little boy born with spina bifida. Eli only lived a few days, but his life is having a significant impact on the world. His mom and dad started project Eli (every life inspires) which is a video distributed to doctors delivering babies, crisis pregnancy centers, hospitals, and other organizations to give to families who are expecting a child with spina bifida. The purpose is to give these couples hope, encouragement and advice from families who have been in their shoes. • Three interior and three exterior pockets to store baby gear and mom's personal items • Adjustable straps allow you to carry the bag three different ways as handbag, shoulder bag, or backpack • Durable high-quality man-made leather outer material is spill proof and wear resistant • Color:Black • $179.00 Thanks for looking and happy bidding!
